      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1775920706922,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Thre is quiet some relationship between the entities and we do need the\nconsitency with the DB - \"Postgress DB\"  shoud work ! \n- ACID Property -> Ensures read happens only after a successful write.\n- Not mandatory but Dynamo DB also supports ACID property (Partially) so yeah that also kind of okay here.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
