      "originalText": "Thre is quiet some relationship between the entities and we do need the\nconsitency with the DB - \"Postgress DB\"  shoud work ! \n- ACID Property -> Ensures read happens only after a successful write.\n- Not mandatory but Dynamo DB also supports ACID property (Partially) so yeah that also kind of okay here.",
